@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Quen mat khau
autonumber
autoactivate on

actor "Nguoi dung" as User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Identity Service" as IDS

User -> FE: Nhap email quen mat khau
FE -> GW: Gui yeu cau lay lai mat khau
GW -> IDS: Chuyen tiep yeu cau
IDS -> IDS: Kiem tra yeu cau va gui OTP neu hop le
IDS --> GW: Tra ket qua
GW --> FE: Tra ket qua
FE --> User: Hien thi man hinh nhap OTP va mat khau moi

User -> FE: Nhap OTP va mat khau moi
FE -> GW: Gui yeu cau dat lai mat khau
GW -> IDS: Chuyen tiep yeu cau
IDS -> IDS: Kiem tra OTP

alt OTP khong hop le
  IDS --> GW: Thong bao dat lai mat khau that bai
  GW --> FE: Tra ket qua
  FE --> User: Hien thi loi xac thuc
else OTP hop le
  IDS -> IDS: Cap nhat mat khau moi
  IDS -> IDS: Huy cac phien dang nhap cu
  IDS --> GW: Tra ket qua thanh cong
  GW --> FE: Tra ket qua
  FE --> User: Chuyen ve man hinh dang nhap
end

@enduml
